title: Sextwister
description:
WE ROCK IT HARD. ACOUSTIC STYLEE. LISTEN AND YOU WILL HAVE NO CHOICE BUT TO JOIN THE SEXTWISTER ARMY. Formed: summer 2002 by Jake and Dave, Jon and Seth can into play a few weeks later. We play lots of open mic nights. People who ordinarily play open mic nights get offended because we disrepsect the sanctity of open mic night. that is our common goal. our holy crusade. to make you uncomfortable and to make you laugh your ass off.

Newly popularized by the Drunken Peasants podcast, used for intermissions
